'''Lancelot Stephen Bosanquet''' (26 December 1903  St. Stephen's-by-Saltash, Cornwall, England – 10 January 1984 Cambridge) was a British mathematician who worked in [[analysis (mathematics)|analysis]], especially [[Fourier series]].

